div.span: According to the current failure phenomena of 220374xxxx, the main manifestation is:

li.span: After Disable LPM, the current measurement value of the product cannot reach the expected current value.
DUT can't be detect/program at YAMS1 or YAMS2.

span.div: DG1 will provide these hardware and help setup this tester.

ol.li: Script send a I2C command to disable DUT's LPM through Arduino,
Script read the current measurement value from the programmable power supply to see whether the current value of the DUT is within the expected current value range.

li.span: If it is not within the range, the PCBA will be judged to “FAIL”.
Otherwise, the PCBA is initially considered to be good.

span.div: For example, for 220374XXXX, with LPM disabled, the current value should be 1.0 ∓ 0.1Amp. Once observed the current out of this range during the high performance testing, it will cause all channels can't be lock.
Will be provided by DG1 engineers.
